Package: libglobalplatform6-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libglobalplatform6 (= ${binary:Version})
Description: GlobalPlatform Smart Card Management Library Dev Files
 GlobalPlatform is a standard for the management of the contents on a smart card.
 Mainly this comprises the installation and the removal of applications.
 The project offers a C library and a command shell.
 These are the development files.

